    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "mouths now that I have a local patch that I removed and re-add, before and after every update of lspconfig.\r\n\r\nThanks a lot.\r\n\r\n... btw, as flow has some much instability between version, I believe that using a global flow-bin isn't a good practice.\r\n\r\nso my \"patch\" was to always use npx which is able to catch to correct version of flow from the project.\r\n\r\n```\r\ncmd = { 'npx', '--no-install', 'flow', 'lsp' }",
